title: MisterMusic Show 321 - new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 321 - 120 minutes. 192kbps MP3 stereo.


On this week's show, new tunes by The Generationals, U2, and another new song from the latest album by the New Pornographers.
Plus a huge alternative rock hit is the 'Oldie of the Week'. A number one hit 20 years ago during September 1994.

And an eclectic mix of indie, alternative, and rock from over 5 decades.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly on Rock XS Radio.
